author: Jason Brennan
title: Life | Watch: The queues for a Hailo in Dublin this morning were shocking
text:
It's days like this that we're glad we can just walk to work.
The rail strikes are a bit of a nightmare this morning, causing massive traffic jams on the roads of Dublin city.
It's tough to put into words how bad they've been, so we'll let this vine from Hailo showing the queues for their cabs do the talking for us.
